<p class="title">Colt Model #727 M4
Carbine Assault Rifle</p>

<p style="text-align:center;"><img src="https://assets.aq2world.com/archive/websites/www.actiongames.co.uk/tnn/guide/m4.jpg" border="0"></p>

<table align="center" class="standard" cellpadding="2">
<tr>
<td colspan="2" bgcolor="green">Statistics</td>
</tr>

